channel.title: How to change when you log in what it says
channel.description:
Well atm im using someone elses source, And im entirely new to coding, (Don't laugh) First off i went into the folder, Ctr+F, Found out where the previous owner had his, Changed it..File+Save, closed it out and pressed compile, Then i go to log in and it doesnt change.
When i compile it it says this, Could this be the problem? server.java:9: cannot find symbol symbol : class Webserver location: class server public static Webserver webserver = null; ^ server.java:30: cannot find symbol symbol : class Webserver location: class server webserver = new Webserver(); ^ Note: stream.java uses or overrides a deprecat Note: Recompile with -Xlint eprecation for de
